        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and slice into quarters</p><p>Add the <strong>lettuce quarters</strong> to a bowl with your<strong> cider vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>dressed lettuce quarters</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1670939078375-x200.jpg",
