            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>herby</strong> <strong>lean</strong> <strong>pork</strong> <strong>patty[ies]</strong> and cook for 5 min on one side then flip the patty and reduce heat to medium-high, cook for a further 5 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Keep pressing the patty down with a spatula to keep flat</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1670939082073-x200.jpg",
