            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, remove the tray with the potatoes from the oven and push the potatoes to one side of the tray</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half and add, cut side down, to the other side of the tray and put back in the oven for 4-5 min to warm through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
