        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the herby lean pork patty[ies] are cooked, transfer to a plate and cover to keep warm – this is your <strong>herby lean pork burger</strong></p><p>Keep the pan (and any remaining oil from the burger!) for the next step</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1670939089039-x200.jpg",
