            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-low heat and add a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Crack your <strong>egg[s] </strong>into the pan and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cover the pan with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p><p>Tip: Give your egg a little shake before you crack for a perfectly centred yolk!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
