    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, fill the<strong> warmed brioche bun </strong>with some <strong>mustard ketchup</strong>, a <strong>herby lean pork burger</strong>, a <strong>fried egg </strong>and a sprinkling of <strong>crispy onions </strong>– this is your<strong> herby lean pork & egg burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>herby lean pork & egg burger </strong>with<strong> </strong>the <strong>crispy paprika potatoes</strong> and the<strong> dressed lettuce quarters</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
